<plot>For over 700 years, the country of Northern Ireland has been plagued by civil unrest. This tension between the Catholics and the Protestants has caused thousands of deaths in the past 30 years alone. This film hopes to raise awareness of this nation's struggles by examining one man's story of the history of the conflict and the potential means to a peaceful resolution.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?064377</url></doc>
